# Prompts

As a Firmware Project Leader, 
I want to have the following prompts
- define project
- create a OnePage Project
- Create a Essential doc
- Create a project chart
- create a project plan,
- create a product backlogs
- create Epic Issue,
- create User Story Issue,
- create Task Issue
- create a project status report
- create a project completion report
- create a rojecg dashboard

As a Firmware Requirements Engineer, 
I want to have the following prompts
- create a System Requirements Specification
- create a Sub-System Requirements Specification
- create a Firmware Requirements Specification
    * define Purpose & Scope
    * define Resonsibilities
    * define References
    * define Terms & Definitions
    * define User characteristics Requirements
    * define System Overview
    * define Functional Requirements
    * define Operational Requirements 
           + Interactions
           + Interfaces
           + Data(s)/Inputs/Outputs
    * define Qualtity Requirements
           +  define Performance Requirements
           +  define Safety Requirements
           +  define Security Requirements
           + define Maintainability Requirements
           + define Portability Requirements
           + define Testability Requirements
           + define Availability Requirements
           + define Reliability Requirements
     * define Non-Functional Requirements
           + define Data Definition and Database requirement
           + define User documentation requirements
           + User maintenance requirements
           + Regulatory/Legal Requirements
    * define Data Dictionary
    * define Alarm/Message Dictionary

- create a Requirements Traceability Matrix

As a Firmware Architect,
I want to have the following prompts
- create a Firmware Architecture Document
    * define Purpose & Scope
    * define Hardware Architecture
    * define Firmware System Environment
    * define Firmware Software Architecture
    * define Functional Decomposition
    * define Hazard Mitigation
    * define Key Algorithms
    * define Interface Mechanisms
    * define Interface Data Structures
    * define Error Handling

As a Firmware Risk Engineer, 
I want to have the following prompts
- create a Firmware Hazard Analysis
- create a Firmware FMEA
- create a Firmware Fault Tree Analysis

As a Frimware Security Engineer,
I want to have the following prompts
- create a Firmware Security Test Plan 
- create a Firmware Security Analysis
- create a Firmware Threat Model

As a Firmware Test Manager, 
I want to have the following prompts
- create a project test plan
- create a sub-system test plan
- create a Test Status Report
- create a Test Completion Report
- create a Test dashboard

